{"title":"登高望远","authors":["顾浩"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":11,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"登高望远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾浩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把酒携卷天街路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步三思四顾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚底松腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶云飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘然不知何处！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭石问古，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将拜岳帝王，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逐个细数。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追昔望远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满怀豪情登高赋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世事纷纷若絮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"料百年岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂无风雨？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妖言弄巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魔计穷恶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎改夜去昼续？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且看人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正红日东升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞光万缕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同凉共暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有中华儿女！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}